Networking devices
——
Hub - layer 1 device
- Collision domain 
Switch - layer 2
- Inspect the data, reduce collision domain

Both are used on single n/w

Router - layer 3
Used on independent n/w’s, used in LAN & WANs
Routing table - to find optimal path

